ted butter, diced"]},{"title":"Cherry Filling","content":["8 oz frozen cherries, pitted, thawed","2 oz sugar","2 tsp lemon juice"]},{"title":"Crepes","content":["2 oz unsalted butter, divided"]},{"title":"Whipped Cream","content":["6 oz heavy whipping cream","1 tsp sugar"]},{"title":"Assembly","content":["chocolate sauce, to drizzle"]}],"id":"r443980","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-tiygr7JMLJA\/XZWZUK04onI\/AAAAAAAAeLA\/U8cwq3ObR3owvAlkCbr6vsoDFCMCOG7xgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ZYtBZeABEEr5YEx8.png","title":"Black Forest Crepes","publishedAt":"2019-02-01T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5 g","fat":"25 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"42 g","calories":"1678 kJ \/ 401 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling wrap, serving platter, skillet (10 in.), refrigerator","basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 15m","6 pieces"]}